entries.s_11: Uh....that isn't exactly a safe location.
entries.s_13: Any advice on what we should do?  We can't stay here and wait it out.
entries.s_15: There is a small camp of survivors near the entrance.
entries.s_17: We'll have to make a run for it then. Cover us if you can. You've done so much for us already, %TU, but I really do not want to become one of them.
entries.s_19: I'll do my best, run for the starport area.
entries.s_21: Will do. Open the hatch when you are ready.
entries.s_23: Let us know when you are ready.
entries.s_25: Look like you dozed off for a few minutes. You must be exhausted. Ready to get out of here?
entries.s_26: Are you stuck down here too?
entries.s_5: It is finally good to see you in person, and in one piece. My name is Doctor Nomi Rhane, good to meet you, %TU.
entries.s_7: Lets get out of here Doctor.
entries.s_9: We'll follow your lead. I have never used this escape ladder but it should take us to the surface right around the entrance of the research facility.
